; Copy this file to "common.local.ini" in this same folder and fill in your
; DEMO account credentials below. common.local.ini is listed in .gitignore —
; it will never be committed. Do not paste its contents into chat, issues,
; commit messages, or logs.
;
; Why this file exists: MT5's command-line Strategy Tester needs an
; authenticated [Common] session to actually run automated tests. Without
; it, terminal64.exe silently opens your normal saved terminal session
; instead of testing — no error, no report, and (as discovered 2026-07-14)
; it can recover/display whatever live or demo positions and pending
; orders already exist on that default session's charts.
;
; Use your DEMO account only. Never put live-account credentials here.

[Common]
Login=YOUR_DEMO_LOGIN
Password=YOUR_DEMO_PASSWORD
Server=YOUR_BROKER_DEMO_SERVER
